{"tid":2264480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩去左家族飯局 00後表妹問電視機個肥婆係邊個？","createTime":"2020-10-30T16:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T10:08:18.000Z","uid":42246,"like":37,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7105a9c34a78496764c442bd9eb40562a3949773","tid":2264480,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"親戚見可以6個人食飯 <br />\n就約左我一家去酒樓食個晚飯<br />\n咁間垃圾酒樓就播tvb<br />\n突然間00後表妹同大家講<br />\n「嘩乜依家d 廣告拍攝成本咁低 用部低清cam搵個肥婆拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就望一望啦 <br />\n頂你個肺 肥姐來既<br />\n有生之年竟然重睇到肥姐賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntvb 2020死人都拎出來消費<br />\n（金象米廣告）<br />\n<br />\n跟著我就笑我表妹 <br />\n<span class=\"red\">全香港娛樂圈最大黑澀會美眉你都唔識？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後表妹 面都紅埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n谷著谷著咁<br />\n我再講多句「哎 依家d 00真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢一句彈埋來<br />\n「係唔識架啦，依d死老野係得死老野先識。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然間 我即刻灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢講得岩 90後真係變左死老野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評：我代表90後肉體上懲罰00後表妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評：90後死老野收皮啦 返去老人屋到老死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8dcb83aa34e508edef6cd14de672205e0755d5","tid":2264480,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d014b69d640b6e99b4e724372a4ab74a8d429187","tid":2264480,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc538b4e13c7a70e90a4de3de4d740680fc1c05f","tid":2264480,"uid":247085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"478f74d026f09eb4538d9bbc837109d9172064d2","tid":2264480,"uid":297241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6edefe38da55602047b572bf692303f64a678589","tid":2264480,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"478f74d026f09eb4538d9bbc837109d9172064d2","tid":2264480,"uid":297241,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:12:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"一定啦<br />\n個個廣告 買左永久"},{"pid":"c3066e59b4c5027bd1f23d11f88f1b70af144d29","tid":2264480,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"戴返個頭盔先 欣宜唔好告我<br />\n我講既黑澀會美眉<br />\n係依d<br />\n<br />\n<im